<p><b>Cognitive science</b> is the interdisciplinary, <a href="/wiki/Science" title="Science">scientific</a> study of the <a href="/wiki/Mind" title="Mind">mind</a> and its processes. It examines the nature, the tasks, and the functions of <a href="/wiki/Cognition" title="Cognition">cognition</a>. Cognitive scientists study intelligence and behavior, with a focus on how nervous systems represent, process, and transform information.
</p>
